ef="regulation-2-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/438/regulation/2/1">reg. 2(1)</ukm:Section></ukm:CommencingProvisions><ukm:CommencingSavings><ukm:Section Ref="regulation-2-2" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/438/regulation/2/2">reg. 2(2)</ukm:Section><ukm:Section Ref="regulation-2-3" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/438/regulation/2/3">(3)</ukm:Section></ukm:CommencingSavings></ukm:InForce></ukm:InForceDates></ukm:UnappliedEffect></ukm:UnappliedEffects></ukm:PrimaryMetadata>



